reviewText: Great movie, good morals, recommend to any parent.

My son who does not like toys enjoys his videos and when given a choice he always chooses AutoBGood - over his favorite Vegetails. I thought he would really like this one but I did not realize that the format varies, he loves the music and music videos and this one does not have any. If you like videos and music I would get AutoBGoods "Life in the Fastlane" versus this video.
The kids have a great time watching their 'cars.'  It's fun and teaches great lessons.  Calli, always makes me laugh too!
